data.text: @Journey_On1 Hope you are able to get it soon. You should have gotten access before me. This roll out has a lot overlooked.

@ZLeeily Thank you for acknowledging this! ❤️ 

I totally agree. We are doing what we can - speaking with Orange County through social media channels and sending letters to FL’s leadership. Cannot hurt to ask. 😊
@Journey_On1 I was wondering how it works for health care providers like you who are working outside a giant hospital system. Seems like it’s easy for you to slip through the cracks
